Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:33.55,Aono edch,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}輕輕地頷首 因為你的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:40.44,Aono edch,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}張大那緊握著的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:44.27,Aono edch,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}一起翱翔吧
Comment: 0,0:24:03.98,0:24:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}什...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.05,0:00:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}怎...麼會...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.67,0:00:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這是開...開...玩笑...的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.29,0:00:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}各務老師說這張紙放在她的桌上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2} 為什麼...
Comment: 0,0:00:18.51,0:01:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,op
Comment: 0,0:01:48.38,0:01:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,staff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:01:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}學姊竟然已經到校了 這樣啊 因為太早起床所以睡眠不足
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}所以才不小心交出了退社申請書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}話說 睡眠不足和退社一點關係都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小真白 妳自己吐槽自己是想怎樣啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯...一大早就在吵吵鬧鬧喵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}學姊 妳不是認真的對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}ㄒ...ㄒ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}香腸嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嘴啦 嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}欸? 嘴...嘴...嘴嘴嘴嘴...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:34.09,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那個 現在可不是玩接龍的時候...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沒想到竟然會被明日香吐槽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2} 好好跟我們說說吧 妳是有什麼打算嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:40.43,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嘴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳有看到這個嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}嗯...就膩了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}早上要早起也好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2} 我們很認真地在問妳喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳們就別管我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}當然要管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}看吧 上課囉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我還會再來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2} 沒回來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}看來是逃走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}有烏龍麵喔 請妳快點出來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}2年C班的鳶澤美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}同學 鳶澤美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}請馬上到學務處來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}搞什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}該不會做了什麼壞事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是為了不要給我們添麻煩 所以才退社的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}咦? 怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}剛才不是被廣播了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}所以我們因為擔心...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不好意思 那是我的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沒想到美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊沒上鉤 妳們兩個卻上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}沒有來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳們聲音這麼大會引起獵物注意的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}確實是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小真白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳還好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}作戰失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我還有方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}準備執行美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊捕獲作戰 第二彈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}作戰之一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}首先 鐘聲一響 明日香學姊和{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}窓{\r\blur2}果學姊就到教室的前後門去堵人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那麼 今天就到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那個...可以借過一下嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 被她逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}鳶澤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}社長 不 前社長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是因為我引退的關係 害妳受到打擊了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:54.29,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那...個...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}老哥 我覺得那絕對不是原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}什...什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那她退社的理由...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}屋頂?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}要飛囉喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}上面?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}從規定外的地方起飛可是違反校規的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我為什麼要逃跑啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:07:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2} 請妳等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}為什麼要放棄?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}發生什麼事了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我今後也想和小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}一起繼續飛下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我已經...無法飛翔了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}總覺得啊 這越來越無趣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香妳就好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明明才剛開始練沒多久 就和真藤同學比了場這麼棒的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}秋季大賽妳也要出場吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好了 快去練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}無法飛翔?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}她說覺得越來越無趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那就把這裡改成能讓學姊覺得有趣的社團吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:07:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}具體來說?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}FC烏龍麵社之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那是什麼鬼社團啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就是 下雨天就吃烏龍麵的社團
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}FC糠床社呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}早上睡覺FC社
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}遊戲FC社
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這不都是只有小真白妳會有興趣的社團嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}別管她了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}別再逼迫美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}反正 就算我們去逼美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2} 她大概也不會聽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}而且 搞不好她過幾天就回心轉意了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}話說 我還以為小真白妳也會一起退社呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我想要變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}而且我們也被前社長託付要取得區大賽優勝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就是啊 努力地練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:09:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}唯有聚沙才能成塔 某位有名的棒球選手也這麼說過喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好的 新人社長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}簡直就像米一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是說我的皮膚跟米一樣白嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}覺得越來越無趣了...嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}怎麼可能會突然有這種想法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我才在想說 社員終於增加了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沒有理由強迫她繼續參加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}要不要退社 就讓她自己決定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不過 晶也你應該多少能了解鳶澤的感受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳會做什麼給我吃呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳就好好期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}咦? 用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}時間應該還可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}也來買東西嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我們家今天大人都出門了 我是來買晚餐的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}晶也你 為什麼不對我說些什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}也是 反正少了我也無所謂嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}還有其他優秀的選手在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}別說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}抱歉 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我要開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這是飛魚高湯做的咖哩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 這個福神漬和辣韭 也都是我親手做的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}盡量吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}多謝招待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那麼 明天見...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}幹嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}剛才 妳問我為什麼我什麼都不說對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}因為 我多少能了解美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}妳的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}因為 我也逃離了FC的世界
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,cm
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我是在國小時開始玩Flying Circus
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我從來沒輸過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}也在全國大賽獲得優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}剛開始只是單純覺得能在天上飛很有趣 而享受著FC
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但 自從我被選為世界大賽的代表後 我開始害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}人只要認真去看待某件事 就一定會感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}怕事情不順利 怕敗北 還有 怕出現比自己還要厲害的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}當我開始有這種想法之後 飛行就變得一點也不有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}就在那時 有個FC新手的男孩對我提出了比賽的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}令人難以置信地 我輸掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}感覺就像看到了自己的極限一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那之後 我就決定要放棄FC了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不 我覺得放棄的理由是什麼並不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}總之 我逃離了FC的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}在我放棄後 也體悟到了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那就是 持續逃避也是件痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2} 果然還是沒什麼精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}連在吃烏龍麵便當的時候 都感覺她心不在焉的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}面對烏龍麵還那麼消極的學姊 我還是第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}連明日香學姊都...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我在想 小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}說覺得飛行越來越無趣了 到底是什麼意思呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}什麼東西啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}為什麼會有直升機來我們學校?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}艾瓦隆...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}發生什麼事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}事件?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}拍電影吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}老師 發生什麼事了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}突然前來打擾真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}其實我們現在正想申請一場和沙希的練習賽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}比賽?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}和乾同學比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}請問您願意接受嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不 不行 太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我想比
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}倉科
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}決賽的時候她超厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳是?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我是倉科明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 是在第三回戰和真藤比的對手吧? 還請妳務必與我們一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沙希也一起拜託一下人家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}倉科
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}如果感到難受的話 要馬上和晶也說喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這只是練習賽 絕對不要勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊...是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香 直接飛到第二飛行線 然後積極地去接觸對手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}把她拉進纏鬥中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}總之 盡量去攻擊她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}竟然能和乾同學比賽 我好興奮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}啊 在比賽前說這種話真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那麼 全國大賽優勝的乾選手和
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}非常可惜在第三回戰落敗 但卻擁有無限潛能的倉科選手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}兩位的練習賽 終於要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}妳為什麼擅自開起實況了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沙希 讓她瞧瞧我們美麗的FC吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是 伊莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}比賽開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}一比零 首先由乾選手先馳得點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沙希 鳥籠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\fs30\pos(1035,975)}{\blur2}Birdcage
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是 伊莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}哎呀 乾選手 竟然在遙遠的上空停了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}果然 想讓局勢和真藤同學那時一樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}倉科只能從下方去進行對自己不利的纏鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}然而 就算她想在交會時轉移目標去碰浮標
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}也一定是乾會比較快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}但再這樣下去的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}先行抄截的倉科選手 在與乾選手交會或有所接觸前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是無法去觸摸下一個浮標的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}教練
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}用High Yo Yo往乾的正下方飛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}正下方?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}如果乾有所動靜的話 我會告訴妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}到時候妳再用Air Kick Turn往反方向切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這樣應該就能夠跟上乾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我知道了 我要上囉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}她行動了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}哪裡都好 總之先去碰乾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}教練 不管怎麼攻擊 乾同學她都...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這到底是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不管從哪裡攻擊 都一樣會被彈回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這是怎麼回事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:19:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}乾一直在用相同的角度把倉科往下彈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}怎麼會? 那只是巧合...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不對 那是經過完美的計算後所做出來的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}把距離拉開 這樣下去只會讓身體疲勞而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}乾同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}為什麼呢? 乾選手 對手的背後明明破綻百出 卻不去得分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}覺得如何啊? 這完美又美麗的FC
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}您所留下的東西 我們幫您完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香 做假動作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不光是左右 上下的幅度也要做出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不...不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}不管往哪裡飛 乾同學都跟在我上面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我找不到出口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}完美地控制對手的行動 只靠不斷飛行來奪取對手的體力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}鳥籠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\fs30\pos(960,975)}{\blur2}Birdcage
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}還真是名符其實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}時間還剩一分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沙希 到最後一刻都不要鬆懈 劃個完美的句點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}是 伊莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}沒有出口的話 就只好去硬做一個了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香 用Air Kick Turn去撞乾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}這個距離的話 應該能打亂她的姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}哎呀 我真是完全不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}連小美{\fn DFGPOP1-W3 \fs 60}咲{\r\blur2}都濕掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}快點去洗個澡 換個衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}然後我們再一起去吃烏龍麵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那 快點回學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:22:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}也...也是呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我...
Comment: 0,0:22:15.27,0:23:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,ed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.61,0:23:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}我覺得那一定是「請務必要這樣」的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.53,0:23:49.69,up,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}才不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}那就快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.32,0:23:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}答案就在那片天空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.91,0:23:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur2}
